Detailed Description

QoS policies supported by a com.rti.dds.topic.Topic entity.

You must set certain members in a consistent manner:

length of com.rti.dds.topic.TopicQos.topic_data .value <= com.rti.dds.domain.DomainParticipantQos.resource_limits .topic_data_max_length

If any of the above are not true, com.rti.dds.topic.Topic.set_qos and com.rti.dds.domain.DomainParticipant.set_default_topic_qos will return com.rti.dds.infrastructure.RETCODE_INCONSISTENT_POLICY and com.rti.dds.domain.DomainParticipant.create_topic will return NULL.

Entity:
com.rti.dds.topic.Topic

QoS Policies allowed ranges within each Qos.
